'''Level 3301''' was a docking level in [[Byblos/Legends|Byblos]] [[Byblos Starport Tower 214|Starport Tower 214]]. The local [[Imperial Office of Customs/Legends|Imperial Customs]] office was situated at this level, as was [[docking bay 789012634]]. The [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[U-THR]] created some commotion at this level when he attempted to free [[Crimson|his owner]] from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] authorities.

